Required Qualifications And Competencies

* Bachelor’s in Finance with demonstrated capability in cost analysis and 3+ years of experience in a manufacturing environment or;
* Bachelor’s in Engineering with 3+ years of experience in a manufacturing environment and demonstrated aptitude for financial analysis, and;
* Experience with SAP is required;
* Excellent analytical and conceptual thinking skills;
* Experience partnering with site leadership, willing to engage people from all levels in order to increase cost awareness of the site;
* Excellent written and verbal communications skills, and strong interpersonal skills;
* Experience creating detailed reports and giving presentations;
* Autonomous and able to work with cross functional teams;
* Commitment to uncompromising accuracy in data management;
* Ability to think critically, and manage multiple tasks and priorities;
* Ability to prioritize, manage time independently, set objectives and milestones.

Preferred Qualifications And Competencies

* Experience with Microsoft Power BI;
* Proficiency in Google Sheets and Google Slides;
* Experience communicating with senior management / senior organizational stakeholders.

